title: BAP delegation calls on PM
content:
ISLAMABAD, Jun 28 (APP):A delegation of Balochistan Awami Party ( BAP) Sunday called on Prime Minister Imran Khan.
The delegation included Zubaida Jalal, Ehsanullah Reki, Khalid Hussain Magsi, Muhammad Israr Tareen and Rubina Irfan, PM office media wing said in a press release.
Minister for Foreign Affairs Makhdoom Shah Mahmood Qureshi, Defence Minister Pervez Khattak, Education Minister Sahafqat Mahmood,
Deputy Speaker National Assembly Muhammad Qasim Suri and PTIâ€™s Chief Whip Malik Amir Dogar were also present on the occasion.
